**Calculate the frequency response and plot it:**

<<fig = True, caption = "Frequency response of an 11 point moving average filter.">>=
w, h = mfreqz(b)
#Plot the function
plot(w,h,'k')
ylabel('Amplitude')
xlabel(r'Normalized Frequency (x$\pi$ rad/sample)')
show()
